Question
10:
Hospital Patient Risk Classification
Scenario:
A hospital classifies patients as:
High Risk → BP > 140 AND Sugar > 200
Medium Risk → BP 120 140 OR Sugar 140 200
Low Risk → Otherwise
Question:
Implement this classification using R.
Answer:
bp <- 150
 
sugar <- 210
if(bp > 140 & sugar > 200){
risk <- "High Risk"
} else if((bp >= 120 & bp <= 140) | (sugar >= 140 & sugar <= 200)){
risk <- "Medium Risk"
} else {
risk <- "Low Risk"
}
print(risk)
